publicwhip.spmotion: *S3M-3526 Gil Paterson: Roundabout Improvements in West Dunbartonshire—That the Parliament notes the need for improvements to the traffic flow at Kilbowie roundabout and Hardgate Cross roundabout; welcomes the fact that West Dunbartonshire Council recognises the continued problems associated with traffic in this area, and encourages it in its efforts to tackle the problems.

S3M-3526 Roundabout Improvements in West Dunbartonshire (lodged on 24 February 2009) Jamie Hepburn*, Anne McLaughlin*, Bob Doris*, Alasdair Allan*, Christina McKelvie*, Kenneth Gibson*, Aileen Campbell*, Sandra White*, Stuart McMillan*
S3M-3526 Roundabout Improvements in West Dunbartonshire (lodged on 24 February 2009) Des McNulty*, Jackie Baillie*
